  "description": {
    "zh": "下午好，我非常需要得到 TerraGroup 实验室的全套钥匙卡，这件事非常紧急。但你也知道，哪怕是最基础的门禁卡片现在也价比黄金，遑论其他同行权限更高的区域了。我听说 Mechanic 愿意用钥匙卡换取军用装备，但我现在抽不出人手去搜集那些东西。这是事关生死的头等大事，你能出手帮帮我们吗？",
    "en": "Good afternoon. I desperately need the staff keycards from the TerraGroup laboratory, and you know full well how impossible it is to get even one of those. I heard that Mechanic is willing to trade the cards for some military equipment, but I lack the manpower to gather it currently. This is a matter of life and death. Will you help?"
  },
